profile: Penticton Lock and Key is the Okanagan's #1 lock shop with over 40 years of experience and 4 fully licensed Journeymen locksmiths. Our newly renovated and spacious showroom is located right on Main st, within walking distance from the beach. We carry a wide variaty of locks, safes, padlocks and keys including sidewinder and transponder keys to help serve you better. Whether it's a lock repaired, re-keyed, or your house or vehicle opened we can be there to handle all your lock needs. We are the lock and open up specialist.
service_area: Night or day we can be there. We offer the fastest 24 hour service around!
